<p>We paint all types and sizes of commercial vehicle, plant, and equipment from; car derived vans, trucks, trailers, tankers, and machinery. Vehicles are stripped, thoroughly cleaned and prepared by hand prior to painting, in one of our three commercial low-bake ovens. We can undertake fleet work and one-off special requests.</p>
